data.description: Escape to serene country living in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of the countryside.  Situated on 1 acre of a partially wooded lot, this picturesque property offers a perfect blend of rustic charm and privacy.  This country home epitomizes the allure of rural living while being conveniently located within a few miles of Lake James State Park and the lovely town of Marion NC . Whether you seek a weekend getaway or yearn for a permanent escape to a peaceful countryside setting, this property offers the quintessential retreat to call home.
